\displaystyle\bar{x}=\sum_{i=1}^n{x_ip_i}
\sum_{i=1}^n{p_i\left(x_i-\bar{x}\right)^2}=\frac{1}{2}\sum_{i=1}^n\sum_{j=1}^n{p_ip_j\left(x_i-x_j\right)}^2
\displaystyle \left(\sum_{i=1}^n p_ix_i^2\right)-\bar x^2
X
X_1,X_2
 V[X] = \frac{1}{2}E[(X_1-X_2)^2]. 
 \begin{align*} E[(X_1-X_2)^2] &= E[((X_1-E[X])-(X_2-E[X]))^2] \\ &= E[(X_1-E[X])^2] + E[(X_2-E[x])^2] + 2E[X_1-E[X]]E[X_2-E[X]] \\ &= 2V[X]. \end{align*} 
